text: Aditi Aarya (born 13 October 1996) is an Indian actress and singer who works in Indian movies. She won the Femina Miss India beauty pageant and made her acting debut in the Punjabi movie Aape Pein Siyaape. She later played lead roles in Munda Rockstar and Khaao Piyo Aish Karo.
